Well Well Well, what have we here? Anyways, this day has been forever....... and a day. 
I woke up at like 6:30 for no apparent reason. Well, I guess it was a good thing because I have had to do so much cleaning. You see, on saturday my mom hurt her foot, so today she went to the doctors and found out that she broke it! So she isnt supposed to do much, therefore I pretty much have to do it all. Its not that big of a deal, but I feel all grown up. Well, actually not really me and my brother had to go to the store for my mom and shoot we couldnt find anything we had to call her like 5 times.
Good thing the day is going to end soon. Another reason it probably took so long is because I cant wait for tomorrow. Im going to one of my favorite places on earth(No its not Disneyland)SIX FLAGS!!!! man I love that place. 
Well good bye

well as you have probably read in other peoples journal, I went to fine arts this weekend! It was alot of fun. I competed in 5 things, 2 bands, a small human video, a large human video, and a large drama. so now that you know what I did I will tell you how it started. On friday I didnt go to school at all, then at about 12 we left the church. We probably arrived at the hotel at about 2 or so. Then we were all bored so we made this hilarious movie. Then it was time to go to the church. Once we got to the church, I started feeling a bit nervous because for our drama we had to perform I had to memorize this verse and I was so scared that I would forget it! And the fact that our band was performing the song that I was the most nervous about first. But it was cool. 
Then the next day. First I had to  do my small human video, Then after along time and after lunch we did our christan band song. Right after we did our large human video. Then it was time for them to announce the winners. Our large drama made it to the next round so during summer we will be going to Texas!!! It wasnt till after that it hit all of us that we made it! then we were all going crazy, it was fun. then we came home,and I went to church yesterday. well stay tuned for next times broadcast!

all in all it was a very nice wedding. Now I am tired so i am go to bed.
